               ServiceFacilitySets — the CORE of reservation policy
               
               These define WHAT facilities are available on a service
               and WHETHER reservation is required, recommended, or not.
               
               ServiceJourneys link to these via JourneyPart > facilities >
               ServiceFacilitySetRef.
               ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ -->
